    "description": {
      "value": "<p><b>Source</b> <em>Adventurer's Armory pg. 5</em>, <em>Legacy of Fire Player's Guide pg. 23</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><b>Cost</b> 5 gp <b>Weight</b> 2 lbs.</p><p><b>Damage</b> 1d3 (small), 1d4 (medium); <b>Critical</b> x2; <b>Range</b> 50 ft.; <b>Type</b> B; <b>Special</b> -</p><p><b>Category</b> Ranged; <b>Proficiency</b> Exotic</p><p><b>Weapon Groups</b> Thrown</p><h3>Description</h3><p>This curved, scooped-shaped, 2-foot-long wicker basket attaches to your wrist, allowing you to throw fist-sized stones at great speed merely by whipping your arm forward. Loading a sling glove is a free action that does not provoke an attack of opportunity so long as you have a free hand. You take -4 penalty when throwing a stone at an adjacent target and cannot use the weapon to attack creatures in your space.</p>"
